        <div class="advisor-role">Biopharmaceutical executive &middot; board director &middot; executive leadership coach</div>
        <p>Dr. Janet Loesberg, PharmD, is a biopharmaceutical executive, board director, and executive leadership coach with more than 30 years of experience building and leading global medical affairs and R&amp;D organizations. She has held senior leadership positions at Blueprint Medicines, Janssen (J&amp;J), Bristol Myers Squibb, and Pfizer, where she led global teams, supported the development and launch of more than 15 medicines, and advanced innovative therapies for patients with rare diseases and cancer.</p>
        <p>Dr. Loesberg currently serves on corporate and nonprofit advisory boards and consults with biotechnology companies on medical and company strategy, organizational development, and commercialization. She brings a passion for advancing science and improving the lives of patients living with complex and rare conditions.</p>
