        <div class="advisor-role">Executive coach &middot; former psychiatrist &middot; venture investor</div>
        <p>Dr. Elyse Weinstein, MD, is an executive coach, former psychiatrist, Chief of Mental Health, and Medical Director of Physician Recruitment. She is a venture investor dedicated to empowering professionals in the medical field and beyond.</p>
        <p>With extensive experience in leadership, career development, and strategic operational roles, Elyse is both a coach and consultant to new leaders and physicians looking to make significant career decisions and navigate organizational and personal challenges. As a consultant she has provided valuable insight from her 30 years in mental health, experience in a large medical organization, and talent acquisition.</p>
